\c 15
\s Ilizwe elanikwa isizwe sakoJuda
\p
\v 1 Lenkatho yesizwe sabantwana bakoJuda ngokwensendo zabo yayisemngceleni weEdoma\x + Nani 34.3.\x*, inkangala yeZini ngeningizimu\x + Nani 33.36.\x* ephethelweni eningizimu\x + 12.3.\x*.
\v 2 Lomngcele wabo weningizimu wawusuka ephethelweni loLwandle lweTshwayi, kusukela ethekwini elikhangela eningizimu\x + Nani 34.3.\x*.
\v 3 Waphuma waya eningizimu emqansweni weAkirabimi, wedlulela eZini, wenyuka usuka eningizimu kusiya eKadeshi-Bhaneya, wedlulele eHezironi, wenyukele eAdari, uphendukele eKarika\x + 15.47. Nani 34.5.\x*,
\v 4 wedlulele eAzimoni\x + 15.47. Nani 34.5.\x*, uphumele esifuleni seGibhithe; lokuphuma komngcele kwakuselwandle. Lo uzakuba ngumngcele wenu eningizimu.
\v 5 Njalo umngcele wempumalanga wawuluLwandle lweTshwayi, kusiya ephethelweni leJordani. Lomngcele ehlangothini lwenyakatho wasukela ethekwini lolwandle, kusukela ephethelweni leJordani.
\v 6 Lomngcele wenyukela eBeti-Hogila\x + 18.19,21.\x*, wedlula kusuka enyakatho kusiya eBeti-Araba\x + 18.18,22; 15.61.\x*; lomngcele wenyukela elitsheni likaBohani indodana kaRubeni\x + 18.17; 15.37.\x*.
\v 7 Lomngcele wenyukela eDebiri\x + 15.15.\x* kusuka esihotsheni seAkori\x + 7.26.\x*, usiya enyakatho ukhangele eGiligali, omaqondana lomqanso weAdumimi\x + 18.17; 15.37.\x*, ongeningizimu kwesifula. Lomngcele wedlula usiya emanzini eEni-Shemeshi\x + 18.17; 15.37.\x*, lokuphuma kwawo kwakuseEni-Rogeli\x + 18.16. 2 Sam. 17.17. 1 Kho. 1.9.\x*.
\v 8 Lomngcele wenyuka ngesihotsha sendodana kaHinomu\x + 18.16. 2 Kho. 23.10. 2 Lan. 28. 3. Jer. 7.31,32. 19.2,6.\x* usiya ehlangothini lwamaJebusi eningizimu, okuyiJerusalema\x + 15.63.\x*. Lomngcele wenyukela engqongeni yentaba ephambi kwesihotsha seHinomu entshonalanga\x + 17.15.\x*, elisephethelweni lesihotsha seziqhwaga enyakatho\x + 17.15.\x*.
\v 9 Lomngcele wagoba usuka engqongeni yentaba kuze kube semthonjeni wamanzi eNefitowa\x + 18.15.\x*, waphumela emizini yentaba yeEfroni. Lomngcele wagoba usiya eBhahala\x + 15.11,29,60; 19.44; 2 Sam. 6.2. 1 Lan. 13.5,6.\x*, okuyiKiriyathi-Jeyarimi\x + 9.17.\x*.
\v 10 Lomngcele wabhoda usuka eBhahala ngentshonalanga waya entabeni yeSeyiri, wedlulele eceleni kwentaba yeJeyarimi, eyiKesaloni, wehlele eBeti-Shemeshi\x + 21.16. 19.22,38. 1 Sam. 6.9,12. 2 Kho. 14.11. 2 Lan. 25.21,23; 28.18.\x*, wedlule eThiminathi\x + 15.57. 19.43. Gen. 38.12,13. Hlu. 14.1,5; 2 Lan. 28.18.\x*.
\v 11 Lomngcele waphuma uye eceleni kweEkhironi enyakatho\x + 15.45,46. 13.3. 19.43. Hlu. 1.18. 1 Sam. 5.10. 6.17. 7.14. 2 Kho. 1.2,3,6,16. Amos 1.8. Zef. 2.4. Zek. 9.5.\x*; lomngcele wagoba uye eShikeroni, wedlula intaba yeBhahala\x + 15.9.\x*, waphumela eJabineli; lokuphuma komngcele kwakuselwandle.
\v 12 Lomngcele wentshonalanga wawululwandle olukhulu lokhumbi\x + 15.47. 23.4. Nani 34.6,7. Hez. 47.20. Dute. 11.24. 34.2.\x*. Lo ngumngcele wabantwana bakoJuda inhlangothi zonke ngokwensendo zabo.
\s UKalebi unqoba iHebroni leDebiri
\p
\v 13 Wasemupha uKalebi indodana kaJefune\x + 14.13-15.\x* isabelo phakathi kwabantwana bakoJuda, ngokomlayo weN\nd kosi\nd* kuJoshuwa, iKiriyathi-Arba, uyise kaAnaki, eyiHebroni.
\v 14 UKalebi wasexotsha elifeni amadodana amathathu kaAnaki asuke lapho, uSheshayi loAhimani loTalimayi, abantwana bakaAnaki.\x + Nani 13.22. Hlu. 1.10,20.\x*
\v 15 Wasesenyuka esuka lapho waya kwabahlali beDebiri\x + 15.49; 10.38.\x*. Lebizo leDebiri kuqala laliyiKiriyathi-Seferi.
\p
\v 16 UKalebi wasesithi\x + 15.19, Hlu. 1.12-15. 1 Sam. 17.25.\x*: Lowo otshaya iKiriyathi-Seferi, ayithumbe, ngizamupha uAkisa indodakazi yami abe ngumka\add khe\add*.
\v 17 UOthiniyeli indodana kaKenazi\x + Nani 32.12; 14.6,14.\x*, umnawakhe kaKalebi, waseyithumba; wasemnika uAkisa indodakazi yakhe ukuba ngumka\add khe\add*.
\v 18 Kwasekusithi ekufikeni kwakhe wamkhuthaza ukuthi acele kuyise insimu; wasesehla kubabhemi\x + Gen.24.64; 1 Sam. 25.23.\x*, uKalebi wasesithi kuye: Ukhala ngani?
\v 19 Wasesithi: Ngipha isibusiso\x + Gen. 33.11; Josh. 14.13.\x*. Njengoba ungiphe ilizwe elomileyo, ngipha njalo imithombo yamanzi. Wasemnika imithombo engaphezulu lemithombo engaphansi\x + Gen. 21.25; 26.15,18-20.\x*.
